Load balancing: network traffic distribution across servers
- any server: round robin, least connection
- same server: IP hash, sticky session
Polling: periodic synchronous check of external status

Content delivery network (CDN): geographically distributed proxy servers and data centers, availability and performance
Cloud computing: on-demand resources, reduced capital expenses, availability / performance / security / scalability
Cloud engineering: applications for cloud computing
- automation
- containers
- stateless components

WebSocket: simultaneous two-way communication over TCP, compatible with HTTP
